content.howToUseTooltip:
Nin node in taamasiyɛn-cogo dɔw bɛ duguma minnu bɛ Se ka Kɛ ka baarakɛcogo dɔw Sugandi, i n’a fɔ klikɛli, sɛbɛnni dafalenw, a ɲɔgɔnnaw.

Attribut nafa bɛ se ka kɛ duplicated ye app ɲɛ kan. Ni aw ye duplicates sɔrɔ, aw bɛ se ka fɛn wɛrɛw sugandi minnu bɛ se ka kɛ walasa ka danfara dɔn.

Daɲɛ bilenman b’a Jira ko fɛntigiya nafa bɛ Segin, daɲɛ bilenman b’a Jira ko fɛntigiya nafa ye fɛn kɛrɛnkɛrɛnnen ye sisan ɲɛ ɲinini na, wa daɲɛ nɛrɛma b’a Jira ko ɲɔgɔndan segin-segin tɛ Kɛ.
